<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.2">
<l>ampuruva varineṭuṅka ṇalarmakaḷai varaiyakalat tamarntu mallal</l>
<l>kompuruva viḷaṅkaṉimē liḷaṅkaṉṟu koṇṭeṟinta kūttar pōlām</l>
<l>vampalarun taṇcōlai vaṇcēṟai vāṉuntu kōyil mēya</l>
<l>vemperumāṉ tāḷtoḻuvā reppoḻutu meṉmaṉattē yirukkiṉ ṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who worship the feet of our great lord who dwells in the temple</l>
<l rend="indent">which rises to the sky in fertile Cēṟai with cool groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where fragrances waft,</l>
<l>[And] who became like a juggler who took and threw a young calf</l>
<l rend="indent">on fruit of a woodapple [tree] with [well-]shaped strong branches,</l>
<l>Having rested on the slopes of the breasts of the beautiful browed girl</l>
<l rend="indent">whose long, streaked eyes blossom,</l>
<l>They are always in my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
